{"tid":2021193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2020年9月立法會選舉民調","createTime":"2020-05-17T14:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T02:58:21.000Z","uid":322412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24551d1c6d023a19acb36267d4481895f39c40eb","tid":2021193,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"2020年9月立法會選舉，35+許勝不許敗，民主陣營決定全香港5區初選，選出5區的參選隊伍，其餘候選人就一定要選前棄選，同埋幫助其他民主陣營過票+拉票，減低因為互相界票而令到 35+ 失敗。<br />\n<br />\n初選之前想做一下民調，以下嘅潛在候選人，大家覺得邊個會勝出初選呢？<br />\n<br />\n投票規則：每人只可以投1票，投票後不能更改，投票需要登入Gmail，但不會記名。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家廣傳俾你地啲朋友/家人 FB, WhatsApp 群組，幫手投一票!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/uk9m66MmAoMexKCM7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fuk9m66MmAoMexKCM7&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=ae704434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/uk9m66MmAoMexKCM7</a><br />\n<br />\n#立法會 #立法會選舉 #區議員 #區議會<br />\n立法會 立法會選舉 區議員 區議會"},{"pid":"9ec04725b862ef1ba03053b417f360ae35c55080","tid":2021193,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8d4cbfa5c4d166676d37679cb896dc2c10ad967c","tid":2021193,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc0ac1bc234a439229d7a23271777f8f5fd9ba0","tid":2021193,"uid":305014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:58:49.000Z","msg":"lm睇藍碧雲有幾多票"},{"pid":"65045dd3d11b04d82a76913c8a5cc029065fc66e","tid":2021193,"uid":232795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:14:39.000Z","msg":"投左<br />\n建議用bar chart同數字，百分比好過用pie chart <br />\nPie chart好難對邊個打邊個<br />\n<br />\n或者呢個調查，用全票制會唔會更好？"},{"pid":"376e8d0dcf6dd3621e5cb53630f59d4b6b364458","tid":2021193,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"push"}